body:
Meet Elizabeth Bartusiak

Hello! My name is Elizabeth Bartusiak. My favorite colors are orange and yellow because they are so bright and happy! Something you would not guess by looking at me is that I love to play basketball. I play the violin and love to practice often. Last year, I even performed at a wedding!

This is me playing Mozart's Concerto in D Major (Adelaide) in 2013.

Aside from running on the basketball court and making music, I love math. To me, math is like solving complex problems using nothing but logic and shear hope! In the future, you will find me working with computer science to protect other people's security. I also have a creative side...
